## ROUTES

| Route | Description |
|---|---|
| `/` | Homepage — logo + two large links to ESPACES and IDENTITÉS |
| `/espaces` | 3-column grid of all Espaces projects |
| `/espaces/[slug]` | Project detail: sticky left info panel + scrolling right images |
| `/identites` | 3-column grid of all Identités projects |
| `/identites/[slug]` | Project detail: sticky left info panel + scrolling right images |
| `/offres` | Static services/offers page + carousel at bottom |
| `/a-propos` | About page with Emma Reilhac contact info + carousel at bottom |
| `/admin` | Tina CMS editor — DO NOT touch this directory |

