## KEY COMPONENT IMPLEMENTATIONS

### Navigation (src/components/Navigation/)

Fixed top bar, 60px high, z-index: 100.
Logo on the left, four nav links on the right.
Links: ESPACES → /espaces, IDENTITÉS → /identites, OFFRES → /offres, À PROPOS → /a-propos
Active link: color changes to --color-accent (no underline, no transition).
Background: --color-bg (beige). No border, no shadow.

### ProjectCard (src/components/ProjectCard/)

Container: position relative, aspect-ratio: var(--card-aspect), overflow hidden.
Image: width 100%, height 100%, object-fit: cover.
Overlay div: position absolute, inset: 0, background rgba(0,0,0,0.55), opacity: 0 by default.
Title inside overlay: font-family var(--font-heading), color white, bottom-aligned.
On :hover → overlay opacity becomes 1. NO transition property. INSTANT.

```css
/* CORRECT — instant hover */
.card:hover .overlay {
  opacity: 1;
}

/* WRONG — never write this */
.overlay {
  transition: opacity 0.3s ease; /* FORBIDDEN */
}
```

### ProjectGrid (src/components/ProjectGrid/)

CSS Grid, 3 columns, gap: var(--grid-gap).
```css
.grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: var(--grid-gap);
}
```

### ProjectDetail (src/components/ProjectDetail/)

This is the most important layout. It mirrors atelierconcipio.fr/copie-de-saint-denis exactly.

The wrapper is a flex row. The LEFT column is sticky. The RIGHT column is normal flow.
As the user scrolls, the right column moves and the left stays in place.

```css
/* CRITICAL: align-items: flex-start is required for sticky to work */
.wrapper {
  display: flex;
  align-items: flex-start;
  min-height: 100vh;
  padding-top: var(--nav-height);
}

.left {
  position: sticky;
  top: var(--nav-height);
  width: 40%;
  height: calc(100vh - var(--nav-height));
  padding: 40px;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  justify-content: flex-end;   /* meta info sits at the bottom of the panel */
  flex-shrink: 0;
}

.right {
  width: 60%;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: var(--grid-gap);
}

.right img {
  width: 100%;
  height: auto;
  display: block;
}
```

Left column content: project title (--font-heading, large), then meta: year, client.
Meta labels ("Année :", "Client :") use color: var(--color-accent).
Right column: render all project.images as <img> tags, stacked vertically.

### ProjectCarousel (src/components/ProjectCarousel/)

Horizontal row of project thumbnails. Appears at the bottom of:
- /espaces/[slug] (show all projects except current)
- /identites/[slug] (show all projects except current)
- /offres (show all projects)
- /a-propos (show all projects)

NOT in layout.tsx. Rendered inside each page component.

```css
.track {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: row;
  gap: var(--grid-gap);
  overflow-x: auto;
  padding: 0 40px;
  scrollbar-width: none;
}

.track::-webkit-scrollbar {
  display: none;
}

.item {
  flex-shrink: 0;
  width: var(--carousel-thumb-width);
}

.thumb {
  position: relative;
  width: var(--carousel-thumb-width);
  height: var(--carousel-thumb-height);
  overflow: hidden;
}

.thumb img {
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  object-fit: cover;
}

/* same instant hover pattern */
.thumbOverlay {
  position: absolute;
  inset: 0;
  background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.45);
  opacity: 0;
}

.item:hover .thumbOverlay {
  opacity: 1;
}
```

