## IMPLEMENTATION ORDER

Build in this exact order — each phase depends on the previous:

1. **Scaffold** — `npx create-next-app@latest . --typescript --app --no-tailwind --src-dir --import-alias "@/*"` (run inside /website)
2. **Install deps** — `npm install tinacms gray-matter` + `npm install -D @tinacms/cli`
3. **Assets** — copy fonts to public/fonts/, copy logos to public/
4. **tokens.css** — create src/styles/tokens.css
5. **globals.css** — replace default with @font-face + reset
6. **next.config.js** — replace with config above
7. **types.ts** — create src/lib/types.ts
8. **content.ts** — create src/lib/content.ts
9. **Sample content** — create 3 sample .md files per category in content/projects/
10. **Navigation** — build Navigation + Logo components
11. **layout.tsx** — add Navigation, set lang="fr", pad body
12. **Homepage** — src/app/page.tsx
13. **ProjectCard + ProjectGrid** — components + espaces/page.tsx + identites/page.tsx
14. **ProjectDetail** — component + both [slug]/page.tsx files
15. **ProjectCarousel** — component, add to detail pages + static pages
16. **Offres page** — static content
17. **À Propos page** — contact info + carousel
18. **Tina CMS** — write tina/config.ts, update package.json scripts, test /admin
19. **Vercel deploy** — push to GitHub, connect Vercel, set env vars

