## WHEN CREATING ANY NEW COMPONENT

Checklist:
1. Create src/components/[Name]/[Name].tsx
2. Create src/components/[Name]/[Name].module.css
3. Add prop types to src/lib/types.ts if not already there
4. Import in consuming file as: `import [Name] from '@/components/[Name]/[Name]'`
5. Check: does any CSS contain `transition`? If yes, delete it.

